OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGladiators battled in      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBritain, evidence suggests 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Gladiator fights were once staged in   
OL,6, Roman-occupied Britain, new research   
OL,7, suggests.                              
OL,9,FTests have proven that the Colchester  
OL,10,FVase - an ancient artefact which       
OL,11,Fdepicts a fight between combatants -   
OL,12,Fwas locally made and decorated.        
OL,14,FWith no written information, this was  
OL,15,Fthe "only evidence" of such duels in   
OL,16,FBritain, the head of Colchester and    
OL,17,FIpswich Museums told The Observer.     
OL,19,FThe findings have led to "startling new
OL,20,Fconclusions", Frank Hargrave added.    
